🧠 Key Insight

The challenge is dynamically maintaining the largest free interval while obstacles are continuously inserted.

Using:

Ordered Set → locate neighboring obstacles
Segment Tree → maintain maximum gap lengths

allows every operation to be processed efficiently in logarithmic time.

